# Feature Audit - Fisheries App

This document tracks the current implementation status of all features in the Fishery App.

## 🟢 Fully Working
Features that are end-to-end integrated with the backend and ready for use.

| Feature | Description | Status |
|---------|-------------|--------|
| **Geo Suitability** | Real-time map analysis based on State, District, and Water Source. | End-to-end integrated and tested. |
| **ROI Calculator** | Comprehensive economic simulation with subsidy and cash flow. | Fully functional on mobile and backend. |
| **Market Prices** | Live aquaculture commodity prices with trend indicators. | Integrated with backend price database. |
| **Species Intelligence**| Dynamic knowledge base for biological and economic parameters. | Fully integrated with live data. |
| **Water Quality Logs** | Recording and history of water quality measurements. | Integrated with backend persistence. |
| **Equipment Catalog** | Search and filter aquaculture equipment with CAPEX data. | Grid layout implemented and integrated. |
| **Feed Catalog**      | Browse different feed types (Floating, Sinking, Organic) with prices. | Dedicated screen and database table implemented. |
| **Location Services** | Real-time GPS location acquisition and reverse geocoding. | Fully functional using OSM Nominatim. |
| **Backend API Core** | Centralized apiService for communication. | Operational and tested. |

## 🟡 Partially Working
Features that have been started but require more work.

| Feature | Current State | Missing Parts |
|---------|---------------|---------------|
| **User Profiles** | Management of farmer and pond profiles. | Basic UI exists, registration sync logic pending. |

## 🔴 Not Working / Next Steps
Features currently in development or planned.

| Feature | Description | Status |
|---------|-------------|--------|
| **Real-time Notifications**| Alerts for water quality thresholds. | Not implemented. |
